@pps_pm
title: President [+ president +] entrusts the PPS to form a government.
go-to: coalition_menu

@peasants_pm
title: President [+ president +] will entrust a Peasant Party to form a government.
go-to: coalition_menu

@zln_pm
title: President [+ president +] entrusts the ZLN to form a government.
view-if: zln_attempt < 1 and (president_relation <= 59 or (zln_sj > pps_sj or zln_sj > (psl_w_sj + psl_p_sj)))
go-to: zln_menu

@nogov
title: The Sejm is paralyzed.
view-if: zln_attempt >= 1 and pps_attempt >= 1 and psl_w_attempt >= 1 and psl_p_attempt >= 1
on-arrival: failed_forming = 1

The Sejm finds that it cannot establish a mandate, for this reason, the members will reconvene next month for another attempt.

